Old brigand
The old brigand lives in the mountains and keeps tame animals. He has stolen so much in his life, t'would only be fair were he the one to be robbed!
#subobj  1
The abode of the old Brigand
The old Brigand lives in the northern part of the ravine.
#subobj  2
Search the abode of the old Brigand
This old man has been a thief all his life. Why should he not feel how it is to be the victim of theft himself?
